Description:
Mainly squids. Initially a lot more Squid IIs and Squid IIIs but with period Squid Is. Getting to Both Lv3 and Lv4 isn't easy. Lasts up to around 10 minutes if you achieve Lv4.
Surviving over 10 minutes is the goal.
Not tried to see if staying at Lv3 and using homing daggers can get you further. Also has a rapid shrink that ends after 5 minutes, as the end loop starts.
